room_title: Escape room "Riddleston's Final Investigation" by Get Locked Away in Coeur d'Alene
room_address: 1621 N 3rd Street, Suite 500, Coeur d'Alene, ID 83814
room_description: The city is reeling from a crime wave. Chase Riddleston, the lead investigator, got a little too close to identifying the ringleader and was murdered! It's now up to your team to finish what he started, identify the ringleader and stop the crime wave! However, you only have 60 minutes until they strike again, so you must hurry!
